WEBVTT

00:00:00.577 --> 00:00:02.074
Joe Kowan: Imam tremu.

00:00:02.074 --> 00:00:03.567
Uvijek sam imao tremu,

00:00:03.567 --> 00:00:05.395
ne samo malkice,

00:00:05.395 --> 00:00:07.186
već puno.

00:00:07.186 --> 00:00:09.979
Sve do 27 godine to nije bilo važno.

00:00:09.979 --> 00:00:12.537
Tada sam počeo pisati pjesme. Čak i tada

00:00:12.537 --> 00:00:14.339
svirao sam ih samo za sebe.

00:00:14.339 --> 00:00:18.084
Činjenica da su moji cimeri
u istoj kući činila me je nervoznim.

00:00:18.084 --> 00:00:20.891
Ali nakon 2 godine, samo
pisanje pjesama nije bilo dovoljno.

00:00:20.891 --> 00:00:23.910
Imao sam priče i
ideje koje sam želio podijeliti,

00:00:23.910 --> 00:00:27.216
ali nisam mogao psihološki.

00:00:27.216 --> 00:00:30.142
Imao sam iracionalni strah.